'''Iinchou''' (委員長 ''Īnchō'') is a [[Japanese language|Japanese]] term meaning ''class representative''. Commonly depicted in [[anime]] as a bespectacled girl (''[[meganekko]]''). They are often referred to by the other characters in their class solely by their title rather than by their own name. Examples include:
*Hikari Horaki in [[Characters_in_Neon_Genesis_Evangelion#Other_Children_Candidate_Hikari_Horaki|Evangelion]]
*Ayaka Yukihiro in [[Negima]]

